    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Assuming the upper is the upper bound and lower is the lower bound, then you can make a random number, r, between the two bounds with:</p>\n\n<pre><code>int r = (int) (Math.random() * (upper - lower)) + lower;\n</code></pre>\n"
