  "title" : "Java Generate Random Number Between Two Given Values",
  "body" : "<p>I would like to know how to generate a random number between two given values.</p>\n\n<p>I am able to generate a random number with the following:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Random r = new Random();\n\nfor(int i = 0; i &lt; a.length; i++){\n    for(int j = 0; j &lt; a[i].length; j++){\n        a[i][j] = r.nextInt();\n    }\n\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>However, how can I generate a random number between 0 and 100 (inclusive)?</p>\n"
}